{%- comment -%}
  Kaadu font helper.

  Brand fonts (fagies, bantergroteskregular) are declared globally in
  snippets/css-bridge.liquid using direct Shopify CDN URLs, so they are
  available on every page without any extra work. This snippet is kept as
  a no-op placeholder in case that ever changes, and to serve as a
  reminder of where the font loading actually lives.

  Font CDN declarations (in css-bridge.liquid):
    • 'fagies'               — display / H1
    • 'bantergroteskregular' — body / headings (Regular weight)
    • 'bantergrotesk'        — body / headings (Semibold weight)
    • 'thickhead'            — legacy display fallback

  Theme CSS variables (set in theme.liquid → css-bridge.liquid):
    • --heading-font-stack → fagies
    • --main-font-stack    → bantergroteskregular

  kaadu-ds.css references var(--heading-font-stack) and
  var(--main-font-stack), so all kds- components pick up the correct
  fonts automatically.
{%- endcomment -%}
